This is Flourish vesrion 0.0.1
==============================

Flourish is an action game, with strong inspiration from Brandish for Nippon
Falcom.

You need a mouse to play.

Requirements
------------

* Yog 0.0.10
* SDL 1.2.14
* SDL_image 1.2.10
* SDL_mixer 1.2.11
* SDL_ttf 2.0.9

Documentation
-------------

Online documents are at http://SumiTomohiko.github.com/flourish/.

Offline documents are available in the ``doc`` directory.

Download
--------

See http://github.com/SumiTomohiko/flourish/downloads.

Build Instructions
------------------

See ``INSTALL``.

Issue Tracking System
---------------------

You can see the issues at
http://neko-daisuki.ddo.jp/~SumiTomohiko/flourish/issues/index.html.
Original data are in the ``issues`` dicretory of the source tree.

Author
------

See ``AUTHORS``.

